@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Gestion patients

autonumber

actor Receptionniste
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServicePatient as "Service Patient"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Receptionniste -> Frontend: Saisir informations patient
Frontend -> API: POST /patients (fichePatient)
API -> ServicePatient: validerDonnees(fichePatient)
ServicePatient -> DB: Verifier unicite CIN / email
DB --> ServicePatient: Resultat verification

alt Donnees valides
  ServicePatient -> DB: Inserer nouveau patient
  DB --> ServicePatient: idPatient
  ServicePatient --> API: Patient cree
  API --> Frontend: 201 Created + patient
  Frontend --> Receptionniste: Afficher confirmation
else Donnees invalides ou doublon
  ServicePatient --> API: Erreur validation
  API --> Frontend: 400 Bad Request
  Frontend --> Receptionniste: Afficher erreurs
end

@enduml
